{"tid":2267359,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特權法原意保護議員","createTime":"2020-11-02T04:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T12:22:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5f66a3b2fc5aede3a4ef5ac6f6664ef8043c92c2","tid":2267359,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T04:32:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/4NIYMYZBQJHPLAD4Y5KHAIAJ5U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2F4NIYMYZBQJHPLAD4Y5KHAIAJ5U%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxd2UZYMvR53lMa2%2BnKJB5b4%3D&h=974fbe41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2F4NIYMYZBQJHPLAD4Y5KHAIAJ5U%2F&h=d7ea4f5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/4NIYMYZBQJHPLAD4Y5KHAIAJ5U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n特權法原意保護議員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hsQB7XlJ5GNZc2xiBeYV7bfm9Zo=/4138x2725/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GDJCAGABCJHFJAGF7JH2JCOE7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhsQB7XlJ5GNZc2xiBeYV7bfm9Zo%3D%2F4138x2725%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGDJCAGABCJHFJAGF7JH2JCOE7E.jpg&h=7743376b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■楊岳橋指《特權法》原本目的是用作保護立法會議員，但如今卻淪為政權用作打壓民主派議員的武器。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方昨拘捕多名現任及前任立法會議員，提出控罪中最少有兩條涉及《立法會（權力及特權）條例》。身兼大律師的公民黨黨魁楊岳橋指，《特權法》原本目的是用作保護立法會議員，但如今卻淪為政權用作打壓民主派議員的武器。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：建制派奪權主持內會釀混亂  警拘6立會議員 泛民：打壓議會抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者：料搜捕更「進取」<br />\n<br />\n根據陳志全facebook帖文披露，陳被控三條罪中，包括《特權法》第17（c）條的「藐視罪」及一條第19條「干預議員、立法會人員或證人罪」。藐視罪列明，任何人在立會或任何會議引起任何擾亂，令立會或委員會會議程序中斷即屬犯罪；而干預議員、立法會人員或證人罪列明任何人襲擊、妨礙或騷擾任何前往或離開會議廳範圍，或在會議廳範圍內任何議員及立會人員即屬犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n警方去年11月曾以《特權法》拘捕七名議員或前議員，包括。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋回覆查詢指《特權法》用意是保護議員，「而唔係要嚟變成一種武器，去攻擊議員」，指政府秋後算賬，客觀效果是無所不用其極打壓民主派。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0WFq3dJkiB4ux-ciM30l8ueMF38=/1080x890/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q4TYPZD4ONAKVLAQXVJU6HRE3M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0WFq3dJkiB4ux-ciM30l8ueMF38%3D%2F1080x890%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ4TYPZD4ONAKVLAQXVJU6HRE3M.gif&h=8c04ee7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c080508df8b125af8f1e17c38fdcc08ef204a50","tid":2267359,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T04:39:21.000Z","msg":"立法原意係咪都係法庭考量入面架？<br />\n<br />\n利申法律白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3aa4e6132f4163d2db8b0aba5bf1277c4433e9","tid":2267359,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T05:08:02.000Z","msg":"唔俾投訴法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c74b054773a86ad670410ee8e5394a27299b19d","tid":2267359,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"有請公民黨楊岳橋出黎講幾句"},{"pid":"f3919fa67e90ba96dc2127ba35dad7a32a90df8e","tid":2267359,"uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c080508df8b125af8f1e17c38fdcc08ef204a50","tid":2267359,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T04:39:21.000Z","msg":"立法原意係咪都係法庭考量入面架？<br />\n<br />\n利申法律白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T05:10:35.000Z","msg":"以前係<br />\n但依家就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3801c082b170e49fda548504b1a9e6ee1e9cdb75","tid":2267359,"uid":321090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}